-- Russian Apple Retailer Re:Store Buys Operator of Samsung Stores
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-10-03T08:04:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-03/russian-apple-retailer-re-store-buys-operator-of-samsung-stores.html
Re:Store Retail Group ,  Russia ’s
largest operator of monobrand stores that sell products from
 Apple Inc. (AAPL) , agreed to buy ZAO Nosimo, which operates 43 Samsung
stores in the country.  Re:Store is Europe’s largest Apple premium reseller with 69
stores in Russia and 26 in Germany, Norway and Denmark, it said
in an e-mailed statement today. The retailer also operates
stores of Lego A/S, Sony Corp. and  Nike Inc. (NKE)  in Russia.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
 ikhrennikov@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  